hillbillies.common.internal.map

Interface IByteMap3D

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ByteMap3D, EmptyMap

    public interface IByteMap3D
    For internal GUI use only. Interface for an efficient 3D map that notifies listeners when changes are made. Contains byte values.
